algorytm = "C5.0"
epochs = 500
seed = 100
#tune = 500

super = FALSE

library(caret)
library(dplyr)
library(epiDisplay)
library(pROC)
library(ggplot2)

while (super == FALSE) {

set.seed(seed)

  cat(paste0("\n\n----- SEED ", seed ," -----"))
setSeeds <- function(method = "cv", numbers = 1, repeats = 1, tunes = NULL, seed = 1237) {
  #B is the number of resamples and integer vector of M (numbers + tune length if any)
  B <- if (method == "cv") numbers
  else if(method == "repeatedcv") numbers * repeats
  else NULL
  
  if(is.null(length)) {
    seeds <- NULL
  } else {
    set.seed(seed = seed)
    seeds <- vector(mode = "list", length = B)
    seeds <- lapply(seeds, function(x) sample.int(n = 1000000, size = numbers + ifelse(is.null(tunes), 0, tunes)))
    seeds[[length(seeds) + 1]] <- sample.int(n = 1000000, size = 1)
  }
  # return seeds
  seeds
}

cvSeeds <- setSeeds(method = "cv", numbers = 10, tunes = epochs, seed = seed)

#pdf("rplot.pdf") 

#dane = read.csv("metadb.csv")
#dane = dane[,-1]

library(doParallel)
cl <- makePSOCKcluster(detectCores() - 2)
registerDoParallel(cl)

#library(mice)
#md.pattern(dane)

#tempData <- mice(dane,m=1,maxit=500,meth='pmm',seed=500)

dane = read.csv("metadb_complete.csv")

step1 = dplyr::select(dane, meta, age, sex, height, weight, bmi, allergy, starts_with("rs"), starts_with("mac"), FEV1, FVC, FEV1doFVC)
step1c = dplyr::select(dane, meta, age, sex, height, weight, bmi, allergy, FEV1, FVC, FEV1doFVC)
step2 = dplyr::select(dane, meta, age, sex, height, weight, bmi, allergy, starts_with("rs"), starts_with("mac"), FEV1, FVC, FEV1doFVC, TestKontroli, LiczbaZaost, LiczbaPaczkolat, age_of_diagnosis)
step2c = dplyr::select(dane, meta, age, sex, height, weight, bmi, allergy, FEV1, FVC, FEV1doFVC, TestKontroli, LiczbaZaost, LiczbaPaczkolat, age_of_diagnosis)
step2 = dplyr::filter(step2, meta == "1 Mild Asthma" | meta == "2 Severe Asthma")
step2c = dplyr::filter(step2c, meta == "1 Mild Asthma" | meta == "2 Severe Asthma")
step2$meta = as.character(step2$meta)
step2$meta = as.factor(step2$meta)
step2c$meta = as.character(step2$meta)
step2c$meta = as.factor(step2$meta)
step1$meta = ifelse(step1$meta == "0 Healthy","0 Healthy", "1 Asthma")
step1c$meta = ifelse(step1c$meta == "0 Healthy","0 Healthy", "1 Asthma")

train_control <- trainControl(method="cv", number = 10, search="random", classProbs = TRUE,
                              summaryFunction = twoClassSummary, seeds=cvSeeds)

# train the model
a <- createDataPartition(step1$meta, p = 0.8, list=FALSE)
training1 <- step1[a,]
test1 <- step1[-a,]
training1c <- step1c[a,]
test1c <- step1c[-a,]



## Use the same random number seed as the RFE process
## so that the same CV folds are used for the external
## resampling. 


a <- createDataPartition(step2$meta, p = 0.8, list=FALSE)
training2 <- step2[a,]
test2 <- step2[-a,]
training2c <- step2c[a,]
test2c <- step2c[-a,]

training1$meta = as.factor(training1$meta)
training1c$meta = as.factor(training1c$meta)
training2$meta = as.factor(training2$meta)
training2c$meta = as.factor(training2c$meta)

levels(training1$meta) = c("Healthy","Asthma")
levels(training1c$meta) = c("Healthy","Asthma")
levels(training2$meta) = c("Nonsevere","Severe")
levels(training2c$meta) = c("Nonsevere","Severe")

test1$meta = as.factor(test1$meta)
test1c$meta = as.factor(test1c$meta)
test2$meta = as.factor(test2$meta)
test2c$meta = as.factor(test2c$meta)

levels(test1$meta) = c("Healthy","Asthma")
levels(test1c$meta) = c("Healthy","Asthma")
levels(test2$meta) = c("Nonsevere","Severe")
levels(test2c$meta) = c("Nonsevere","Severe")

#featureselection
#devtools::install_github("STATWORX/bounceR")
library(bounceR)
mr1 <- featureFiltering(data = training1,
                            target = "meta",
                            method = "mrmr",
                            returning = "names")
formmr1 = as.formula(paste("meta", paste(mr1, collapse=" + "), sep=" ~ "))
cat("\n\n----- FORMMR1 -----")
print(formmr1)

mr2 <- featureFiltering(data = training2,
                        target = "meta",
                        method = "mrmr",
                        returning = "names")
formmr2 = as.formula(paste("meta", paste(mr2, collapse=" + "), sep=" ~ "))
cat("\n\n----- FORMMR2 -----")
print(formmr2)

model_step1 = caret::train(meta ~ ., data=training1, trControl=train_control, method=algorytm, metric = "ROC",
                           tuneLength = epochs)
cat(paste0("\n\n----- MODEL STEP1 -----"))
print(model_step1$finalModel)
model_step1c = caret::train(meta ~ ., data=training1c, trControl=train_control, method=algorytm, metric = "ROC",
                            tuneLength = epochs)
cat(paste0("\n\n----- MODEL STEP1c -----"))
print(model_step1c$finalModel)
model_step1mr = caret::train(formmr1, data=training1, trControl=train_control, method=algorytm,metric = "ROC",
                             tuneLength = epochs)
cat(paste0("\n\n----- MODEL STEP1mr -----"))
print(model_step1mr$finalModel)

t1 = caret::confusionMatrix(predict(model_step1), as.factor(training1$meta), positive = "Asthma")
v1 = caret::confusionMatrix(predict(model_step1, newdata = test1), as.factor(test1$meta), positive = "Asthma")
cat(paste0("\n\n----- T1 i V1 -----"))
print(t1)
print(v1)

t1c = caret::confusionMatrix(predict(model_step1c), as.factor(training1c$meta), positive = "Asthma")
v1c = caret::confusionMatrix(predict(model_step1c, newdata = test1c), as.factor(test1c$meta), positive = "Asthma")
cat(paste0("\n\n----- T1c i V1c -----"))
print(t1c)
print(v1c)

t1mr = caret::confusionMatrix(predict(model_step1mr), as.factor(training1$meta), positive = "Asthma")
v1mr = caret::confusionMatrix(predict(model_step1mr, newdata = test1), as.factor(test1$meta), positive = "Asthma")
cat(paste0("\n\n----- T1mr i V1mr -----"))
print(t1mr)
print(v1mr)

saveRDS(model_step1, paste0(algorytm,"model_step1.RDS"))
saveRDS(model_step1c, paste0(algorytm,"model_step1c.RDS"))
saveRDS(model_step1mr, paste0(algorytm,"model_step1mr.RDS"))

cat(paste0("\n\n----- T1 ROC -----"))
t1_roc = roc(training1$meta ~ predict(model_step1, type = "prob")[,2])
print(t1_roc)
ci(t1_roc)

cat(paste0("\n\n----- v1 ROC -----"))
v1_roc = roc(test1$meta ~ predict(model_step1, type = "prob", newdata = test1)[,2])
print(v1_roc)
ci(v1_roc)

cat(paste0("\n\n----- t1c ROC -----"))
t1c_roc = roc(training1c$meta ~ predict(model_step1c, type = "prob")[,2])
print(t1c_roc)
ci(t1c_roc)

cat(paste0("\n\n----- v1c ROC -----"))
v1c_roc = roc(test1c$meta ~ predict(model_step1c, type = "prob", newdata = test1c)[,2])
print(v1c_roc)
ci(v1c_roc)

cat(paste0("\n\n----- t1mr ROC -----"))
t1mr_roc = roc(training1$meta ~ predict(model_step1mr, type = "prob")[,2])
print(t1mr_roc)
ci(t1mr_roc)

cat(paste0("\n\n----- v1mr ROC -----"))
v1mr_roc = roc(test1$meta ~ predict(model_step1mr, type = "prob", newdata = test1)[,2])
print(v1mr_roc)
ci(v1mr_roc)

cat(paste0("\n\n----- TESTY ROC -----"))
roc.test(t1_roc, v1_roc)
roc.test(t1c_roc, v1c_roc)
roc.test(t1mr_roc, v1mr_roc)
roc.test(t1_roc, t1c_roc)
roc.test(v1_roc, v1c_roc)
roc.test(t1mr_roc, t1_roc)
roc.test(v1mr_roc, v1_roc)
roc.test(t1mr_roc, t1c_roc)
roc.test(v1mr_roc, v1c_roc)


plot(t1_roc)
plot.roc(v1_roc, add=TRUE, lty=2)
plot.roc(t1c_roc, add=TRUE, lty=3)
plot.roc(v1c_roc, add=TRUE, lty=4)
plot.roc(t1mr_roc, add=TRUE, lty=5)
plot.roc(v1mr_roc, add=TRUE, lty=6)

legend("bottomright", 
       legend = c("Clinical+TGF [training]", "Clinical+TGF [validation]", "Only Clinical [training]", "Only Clinical [validation]", "MRMR [training]", "MRMR [validation]"), 
       lty = c(1:6),
       lwd = 2)

t2 = caret::confusionMatrix(predict(model_step2), as.factor(training2$meta), positive = "Severe")

sink()
if (roc.test(v1mr_roc, v1c_roc)$p.value < 0.05 & roc.test(v1_roc, v1mr_roc)$p.value > 0.05) { 
super = TRUE } else { seed = seed + 1 }
